headline: 3 Tech Stocks Destined to Drive Wealth Now and for Years to Come
summary: Amazon's advertising business alone generated over $56 billion in revenue last year.  The current success of AI is not possible without Taiwan Semiconductor.  The market is overly pessimistic on Alphabet (Google).
